		<node ID="ID_1553296721" LINK="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hamiltonian_path" TEXT="Hamiltonian path - Wikipedia">
			<node ID="ID_1929519150" TEXT="A graph is Hamiltonian-connected if for every pair of vertices there is a Hamiltonian path between the two vertices. A Hamiltonian cycle Hamiltonian circuit vertex tour or graph cycle is a cycle that visits each vertex exactly once. A graph that contains a Hamiltonian cycle is called a Hamiltonian graph." />
